{"tid":204760,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"青色究竟係咩色?","createTime":"2017-04-17T10:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T16:06:27.000Z","uid":39413,"like":7,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b525bd17381a89a1393047a642020e6cb31769","tid":204760,"uid":39413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:02:09.000Z","msg":"明明上網查青色應該係近藍色多啲個隻<br />\n但我發覺日常啲人所指既青色都係近綠色多啲個隻<br />\n究竟邊一隻先係青色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我所了解既青色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Zk94J6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Zk94J6.png&h=32af2136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日常啲人所指既青色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7J64thk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7J64thk.png&h=97d5b4f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f04d6395d944c852bff2dd9f29ffa2c7acd6eec8","tid":204760,"uid":43308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:04:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e8ed9c4d969a0607941a3307bfd0dc7f326efc1","tid":204760,"uid":18516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"其實顏色黎講用英文黎分會清晰好多<br />\n上面個隻係叫cyan"},{"pid":"8767e08ebe56aa976aa0d4c87d695aedaf972e3a","tid":204760,"uid":76488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:05:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e24697de54607c56efea1147f7288c7a527d4f02","tid":204760,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:05:42.000Z","msg":"青天 青草 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057b52a027e4a3df92daf934a825be8446a0bd4d","tid":204760,"uid":94452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你龜頭隻色</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<i