</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e42d46b7f72116777eb6ea9686781c995c10cbe","tid":204760,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"呢個問題我都思考左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓上咪撚騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n青出於藍，明明青色係淺色過藍色，咁點青出於藍呢？"},{"pid":"733f570a98b3bc0f0efed186b84d5a97d149804d","tid":204760,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:19:31.000Z","msg":"古語，甚至日文嘅青係我哋依家所理解嘅藍<br />\n現代嘅青唔知咩原因變咗近綠色嘅色"},{"pid":"bd54e7332bdf5c7db90632a43d6b6589508216b6","tid":204760,"uid":51889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:20:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個問題我都思考左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓上咪撚騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n青出於藍，明明青色係淺色過藍色，咁點青出於藍呢？</blockquote><br />\n藍草可以提取青色<br />\n而青色比藍色更明亮"},{"pid":"44a5ee5b0f07c71cfbdfbebad158ce0e7955f593","tid":204760,"uid":39413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個問題我都思考左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓上咪撚騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n青出於藍，明明青色係淺色過藍色，咁點青出於藍呢？</blockquote><br />\n藍草可以提取青色<br />\n而青色比藍色更明亮</blockquote><br />\n文學上既青多數同年輕健康有關例如青絲<br />\n青年都係指年輕既人<br />\n但唔知係咪因為成日用青黎描寫綠草搞到啲人以為青就係綠色<br />\n但青草個青應該係指健康茁壯<br />\n我理解就咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0be71ce26ae7c256d3a8e0ff19c8218cc588bcd","tid":204760,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個問題我都思考左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓上咪撚騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n青出於藍，明明青色係淺色過藍色，咁點青出於藍呢？</blockquote><br />\n藍草可以提取青色<br />\n而青色比藍色更明亮</blockquote><br />\n文學上既青多數同年輕健康有關例如青絲<br />\n青年都係指年輕既人<br />\n但唔知係咪因為成日用青黎描寫綠草搞到啲人以為青就係綠色<br />\n但青草個青應該係指健康茁壯<br />\n我理解就咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁青色即係咩色<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb1ea185e361091d58dabfd51aae84ef34af7d0","tid":204760,"uid":34308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"上面淺藍<br />\n下面係青<br />\n紅橙黃綠青藍紫"},{"pid":"c5ab0f0020c3747d1443ee81e385bf7139d25130","tid":204760,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:41:39.000Z","msg":"古代嘅青有好多意思<br />\n青天=藍色<br />\n青草=綠色<br />\n青絲=黑色"},{"pid":"beb2d4407caf712726c5db0f680416a03f71b34f","tid":204760,"uid":39413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個問題我都思考左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓上咪撚騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n青出於藍，明明青色係淺色過藍色，咁點青出於藍呢？</blockquote><br />\n藍草可以提取青色<br />\n而青色比藍色更明亮</blockquote><br />\n文學上既青多數同年輕健康有關例如青絲<br />\n青年都係指年輕既人<br />\n但唔知係咪因為成日用青黎描寫綠草搞到啲人以為青就係綠色<br />\n但青草個青應該係指健康茁壯<br />\n我理解就咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁青色即係咩色<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n文學歸文學<br />\n顏色我都唔敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6700a66e856f98535f4097a5da9d58aee3b9e391","tid":204760,"uid":100760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你龜頭隻色</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ae141a98f696762989361c95a210610c9798d1","tid":204760,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:55:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古代嘅青有好多意思<br />\n青天=藍色<br />\n青草=綠色<br />\n青絲=黑色</blockquote><br />\n青天白日滿地紅"},{"pid":"cb8ea5963833e37f71c874f4599758150073a67b","tid":204760,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"